Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:29.86,tanda_srt,,0,0,0,,TENGKORAK EMAS, RAKSASA KABUT UNGU
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:27.10,tanda-6,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,438)\fs80\blur0.5\bord2\shad2\b0\pos(1798,918)}Episode 76: Surat Undangan
